{"tid":1649670,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講定先，唔好比左膠搞到無哂信心","createTime":"2019-10-12T17:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T18:12:17.000Z","uid":264356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8c264ebe36476971c8b3843d622d14be3b89ff36","tid":1649670,"uid":264356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:58:43.000Z","msg":"首先，唔係唔比慶祝，大家都明白成日苦行唔得，求婚慶生日唔係第一次，每次都會由得佢地甚至祝福佢地，今次真係低能，係太子站前面慶祝，完全無尊重過死左手足既左膠，一係道歉一係死撚開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係見到好多人係咁開post，一定要記住大家都好明白失去手足既痛，先至會咁大反應，要保持住依種精神，唔好比左膠搞到散水，要繼續盡做自己本份，聽日有十八開花同摺紙，後日有法案集會，清算左膠等贏左先，好唔好啊大家？"},{"pid":"39bb50f40f3345875a5f6296ce9f14a317c725de","tid":1649670,"uid":264356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:01:37.000Z","msg":"連最基本尊重都無，我傷心到爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係依家無時間同本錢比我地清算左膠，迫佢道歉只係嘥時間"},{"pid":"9355984ae8aebdbcfcd351e63fe2112058d31bc5","tid":1649670,"uid":323520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:01:56.000Z","msg":"真，嬲還嬲<br />\n唔好比帶風向 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32bf730f87ef40cac92a477dddd3b5a3a547aee6","tid":1649670,"uid":264356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9355984ae8aebdbcfcd351e63fe2112058d31bc5","tid":1649670,"uid":323520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:01:56.000Z","msg":"真，嬲還嬲<br />\n唔好比帶風向 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:10:08.000Z","msg":"但係已經阻止唔到，唔知係唔係風向撚已經話前線唔會想為依啲人打生打死，事實係我地要識得淨係屌鳩依班人，唔係既話對家真係會咁樣分化我地"},{"pid":"48b62c83b3